<br>
Yes it says this at the end: <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Just a reminder... respect of posted raid events is subject to the whims of others. If you post a raid event here, and that raid is usurped by others, then so be it.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
