<br>
The difference between a casual raider and a handicapped person is that very rarely does a handicapped person choose to be that way.  People choose to be casual raiders.  If you make that choice, like I have, you live with the mobs you targetted being down... a lot.  I don't blame the more hardcore people, I just move on and deal with it.<br>
<br>
It's not disrespectful to kill a mob that's up because someone posted that they will be killing it three days, an hour, or a minute from now.  If they're there in force, then it's damn disrespectful to kill it.  If they aren't there, that's the price they pay for choosing not to be a hardcore raider.<br>
